1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 25=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(Steal My Woman? I'll Blow You Up)

4
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:15,840
Why did it fail again?

5
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:17,440
I've already tried 101 fuses.

6
00:01:17,440 --> 00:01:19,160
What am I doing wrong?

7
00:01:19,160 --> 00:01:20,480
You talk

8
00:01:21,240 --> 00:01:22,680
like you're fiercer than a tiger,

9
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:25,480
but you're all bark and no bite.

10
00:01:25,880 --> 00:01:27,200
Some people

11
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,640
are nothing but walking bad luck.

12
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:30,200
Misfortune follows them everywhere.

13
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:32,200
If someone hadn't

14
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:34,480
stuck to me like glue,

15
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:38,080
my newspaper and bank
would've already made my little goal,

16
00:01:38,180 --> 00:01:39,750
and I'd be living the good life by now.

17
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:42,040
If you hadn't been so secretive

18
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:43,440
and so suspicious,

19
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:45,640
I would've never gotten involved.

20
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:47,600
Yet here you are,

21
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,440
making a deal with the devil

22
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:50,880
and bringing trouble upon yourself.

23
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,040
Foolish.

24
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,320
Utterly foolish.

25
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,480
I'm foolish?

26
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:58,840
No matter how foolish I am,

27
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:00,750
at least I wasn't stripped
of my title as Crown Prince.

28
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,160
And I wasn't put on
the nation's wanted list

29
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:02,960
by my own brother.

30
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:36,130
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

31
00:02:36,990 --> 00:02:40,160
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

32
00:02:41,170 --> 00:02:42,830
♪Your smile♪

33
00:02:42,830 --> 00:02:44,600
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

34
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:46,360
(Why do I still care about her?)

35
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:48,930
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

36
00:02:49,530 --> 00:02:52,720
♪Yet I stand before you♪

37
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:55,840
It worked!

38
00:02:55,850 --> 00:02:57,820
Just tweak the formula a little,
and it'll become gunpowder.

39
00:02:57,830 --> 00:02:59,520
♪Though fate tries♪

40
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:02,400
♪To make us pass each other by♪

41
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:05,990
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

42
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:07,210
What are you hiding from?

43
00:03:07,740 --> 00:03:09,630
♪As day turns into night♪

44
00:03:10,040 --> 00:03:12,920
Don't tell me you still like me.

45
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:16,890
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

46
00:03:16,890 --> 00:03:18,200
♪Blessed by fate♪

47
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:19,800
Then I'll stab you again.

48
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:22,480
I haven't forgotten

49
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:24,120
how you treated me

50
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,400
when I had lost my memory.

51
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,800
No, thanks.

52
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:30,760
Then again...

53
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:33,000
I guess you're
not a glutton for punishment.

54
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:36,580
♪And wander the world together♪

55
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,440
I wasn't the one
who burned down the bank.

56
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:40,440
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

57
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:41,680
What did you say?

58
00:03:42,980 --> 00:03:45,600
♪Is the brightest moon♪

59
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:46,880
It was Zheng Yuanzhao.

60
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:48,640
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

61
00:03:48,640 --> 00:03:49,800
Has he lost his mind?

62
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,400
His own money was in there too.

63
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:53,080
Do you think he's as foolish as you?

64
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:55,080
He took his money out long ago.

65
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,600
He robbed the robber.

66
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,000
Zheng Yuanzhao,

67
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:00,800
Just you wait.

68
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:03,680
I'm going to blow you up
and get every last coin back.

69
00:04:09,900 --> 00:04:13,900
(Pan Residence)

70
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,320
Have you two lost your minds?

71
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:33,440
Untie me!

72
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:36,080
Well...

73
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:39,520
Your wedding to the Crown Prince
is just around the corner.

74
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:41,400
If the bride goes missing now,

75
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:42,760
I won't be able to answer for it.

76
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:44,640
You coward!

77
00:04:44,650 --> 00:04:46,280
When Zheng Yuanzhao
laid hands on your parents,

78
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:47,760
you didn't dare say a word.

79
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:48,840
What?

80
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:50,680
Now that I'm down,

81
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,080
you're here to rub it in?

82
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:53,360
Never.

83
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,200
Qingqing...

84
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:55,760
Ah, no.

85
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:57,720
Your Highness, the Crown Princess.

86
00:04:58,240 --> 00:05:00,760
You've risen to the top now.

87
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:01,680
Please don't forget

88
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:03,200
the Pan family's kindness.

89
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:04,680
That's right, Qingqing.

90
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:06,280
Once you're with the Crown Prince,

91
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:08,080
put in a good word for us.

92
00:05:08,080 --> 00:05:10,560
After all, without our devoted care,

93
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:12,240
you never would've lived

94
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,800
to receive such a great blessing.

95
00:05:14,100 --> 00:05:16,240
If you want this blessing so much,
you can have it.

96
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:16,880
I do!

97
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:19,560
You two clowns.

98
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:21,520
Once I get out of this,

99
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,120
you're the first ones I'll deal with.

100
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:26,160
As long as it makes you happy,

101
00:05:26,280 --> 00:05:27,800
you can kick me all you want.

102
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:28,680
Go ahead.

103
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,080
Shameless.

104
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:31,880
Get lost!

105
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:32,720
You missed.

106
00:05:32,730 --> 00:05:34,080
Just hang in there a little longer,

107
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:35,760
the Crown Prince
will be here any moment.

108
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:38,200
The Crown Prince has arrived.

109
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:41,960
What are you two doing?

110
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,240
Let me go.

111
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:43,880
(Wedding Procession)

112
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:44,760
Don't move.

113
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:45,800
Qingqing,

114
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:46,880
where's your dowry?

115
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:48,000
Stop disgusting me.

116
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:48,640
Let go!

117
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:53,680
Qingqing,

118
00:05:54,080 --> 00:05:55,600
my residence has everything you need.

119
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:58,400
Once the wedding ceremony is over,

120
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,160
you can move in at once.

121
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:01,120
Coo...

122
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,390
What are you doing, laying an egg?

123
00:06:02,500 --> 00:06:03,600
You may not be good for much,

124
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,990
but you sure changed your tune fast.

125
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:07,600
Come, Qingqing.

126
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:11,800
I'll go.

127
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:14,760
But what about Caiyuan and Jiuzhu?

128
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:22,400
Move.

129
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:25,840
Kneel.

130
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:34,120
Yuanzhao, is this the best you've got?

131
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,440
How predictable.

132
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:36,880
As long as it works.

133
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,600
Once you marry into my residence,

134
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:42,120
whether it's Wangshi Tower

135
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,520
or the Pan family,

136
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,520
I'll let bygones be bygones.

137
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:48,240
If you still resent Pan Yang,

138
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:51,240
I can kill him right now.

139
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:56,640
I know I was wrong.

140
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:00,200
This...

141
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:02,080
This is my repeating crossbow.

142
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,480
That's right.

143
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:06,000
Let Pan Yang die
by the repeating crossbow you designed.

144
00:07:06,300 --> 00:07:08,080
It'll be the perfect way
to settle your grudge.

145
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,960
You stole my blueprints

146
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,680
and didn't even pay me
a single coin in royalties.

147
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,360
Qingqing,

148
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:14,040
you've misunderstood me.

149
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:17,400
I merely had them
recreate the repeating crossbow.

150
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:19,400
It took quite a bit of effort.

151
00:07:22,190 --> 00:07:23,440
The auspicious hour has arrived.

152
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:25,160
Please escort the Crown Princess.

153
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:35,240
Don't move.

154
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:01,720
Father,

155
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:03,880
today,

156
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,260
I shall take Lady Li
as my Crown Princess.

157
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:08,520
It so happens that Your Majesty
has been unwell.

158
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:11,560
May this joyous occasion

159
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,280
help drive away your illness.

160
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:16,360
You jerk! Let go of me!

161
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,320
Qingqing,

162
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:18,280
be good.

163
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,080
Once the wedding is over,

164
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:22,240
I'll release your maid and Jiuzhu.

165
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:24,440
Father,

166
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:27,560
please proceed to the main hall
to preside over Qingqing's wedding and mine.

167
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:45,560
What took you...

168
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,800
Not this again.

169
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:53,560
He.

170
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:55,520
Father!

171
00:08:58,040 --> 00:08:58,840
Yuanhe.

172
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,640
You've finally come.

173
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:03,120
I knew you couldn't let Qingqing go.

174
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,360
Let her go.

175
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,120
You...

176
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:07,440
You arranged this marriage
to force him into the open?

177
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:09,280
Why not kill two birds with one stone?

178
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:12,920
Yuanhe,

179
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:14,160
you came here all alone.

180
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:16,480
No matter how brave you are,

181
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,640
what can you possibly accomplish?

182
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:21,520
Jiang Shuo.

183
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:25,840
Jiang Shuo!

184
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:33,040
Take them away.

185
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:49,240
Your Highness,

186
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:51,160
all the rebels have been subdued.

187
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:58,120
Caiyuan! Jiuzhu!

188
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:58,880
Tower Master!

189
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,960
At least you still have a conscience.

190
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,440
You remembered to save them.

191
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:08,200
You've already
lost your military command.

192
00:10:08,640 --> 00:10:09,720
How is this possible?

193
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:11,680
Too bad you didn't know.

194
00:10:12,040 --> 00:10:14,400
The Inspectorate
answers to only one master.

195
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,240
Even with the Inspectorate,

196
00:10:18,300 --> 00:10:20,400
there's no way
you could've gotten here this quickly.

197
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:21,960
He has gunpowder.

198
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:24,700
One throw,
and it blows everything apart.

199
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:26,520
What good are your troops

200
00:10:26,880 --> 00:10:27,880
if they're all wiped out?

201
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:31,560
Yuanhe,

202
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:33,280
the person you hate most

203
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:35,800
is also the one you love most.

204
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:37,920
How does that feel?

205
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:43,440
Didn't you hate her?

206
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:46,440
Then today, I'll kill her for you.

207
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:51,400
Zheng Yuanzhao, don't take this too far!

208
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,600
I've lost my mind?

209
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:58,320
I just can't stand the sight of him.

210
00:10:58,640 --> 00:10:59,880
You made such a grand spectacle.

211
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,680
If you want her to live,

212
00:11:03,690 --> 00:11:04,600
then the two of you...

213
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:06,560
one lives,

214
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,840
one dies.

215
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:13,360
What exactly are you trying to do?

216
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:30,900
You've been walking around
with that gloomy face.

217
00:11:31,500 --> 00:11:33,440
I've been sick of looking
at you for a long time.

218
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:38,040
You've been following
Qingqing around every day.

219
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,840
I've been sick of you
for a long time too.

220
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:44,240
What are you two doing now?

221
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:45,720
Fine then.

222
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:47,800
Let's

223
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:50,880
- settle this.
- Settle this.

224
00:11:56,840 --> 00:12:00,230
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

225
00:12:00,990 --> 00:12:04,370
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

226
00:12:05,140 --> 00:12:06,880
♪Your smile♪

227
00:12:07,140 --> 00:12:09,430
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

228
00:12:09,430 --> 00:12:13,110
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

229
00:12:13,570 --> 00:12:16,880
♪Yet I stand before you♪

230
00:12:17,620 --> 00:12:21,450
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

231
00:12:21,870 --> 00:12:23,790
♪Though fate tries♪

232
00:12:23,790 --> 00:12:26,370
♪To make us pass each other by♪

233
00:12:26,590 --> 00:12:30,010
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

234
00:12:30,270 --> 00:12:31,900
♪Though time slips by♪

235
00:12:31,900 --> 00:12:33,660
♪As day turns into night♪

236
00:12:34,180 --> 00:12:38,200
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

237
00:12:38,620 --> 00:12:41,000
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

238
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,790
♪Blessed by fate♪

239
00:12:42,790 --> 00:12:47,950
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

240
00:12:47,950 --> 00:12:50,390
♪Your smiling face♪

241
00:12:50,390 --> 00:12:53,230
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

242
00:12:53,230 --> 00:12:56,850
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

243
00:12:57,370 --> 00:13:00,830
♪And wander the world together♪

244
00:13:00,830 --> 00:13:02,170
♪Holding you close♪

245
00:13:02,170 --> 00:13:04,710
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

246
00:13:04,710 --> 00:13:07,030
♪Your tenderness♪

247
00:13:07,030 --> 00:13:09,890
♪Is the brightest moon♪

248
00:13:09,890 --> 00:13:13,590
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

249
00:13:14,110 --> 00:13:17,400
♪Our love will never fade away♪

250
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:19,860
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

251
00:13:20,390 --> 00:13:24,640
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

252
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:36,280
♪Your smiling face♪

253
00:13:36,460 --> 00:13:39,070
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

254
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:43,230
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

255
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:46,950
♪And wander the world together♪

256
00:13:46,950 --> 00:13:48,270
♪Holding you close♪

257
00:13:48,270 --> 00:13:50,900
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

258
00:13:50,900 --> 00:13:53,160
♪Your tenderness♪

259
00:13:53,160 --> 00:13:56,030
♪Is the brightest moon♪

260
00:13:56,030 --> 00:13:59,770
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

261
00:14:00,210 --> 00:14:03,570
♪Our love will never fade away♪

262
00:14:03,570 --> 00:14:06,220
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

263
00:14:06,490 --> 00:14:10,630
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪
